latestIgtvVideos.title: Dark neck causes and treatment Hindi
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#darkneck #AcanthosisNigricans #DarkNeckTreatment
Causes of darkening in neck area

This is a common complaint in our population.  Causes:
Acanthosis nigricans: darkening with thickening of skin, skin tags 
Friction: wearing chains at sleeping at night.
Stiff collar rubbing against neck
Over weight: BMI more than 25 . 
Sun tanning
 Lichen planus pigmentosus 
Dermatitis neglecta
Eczema  Drug induced pigmentation. 
How to prevent
 Keep weight under check
 Do not wear chains while sleeping
 Do not scrub 
Use a sunscreen

Evaluation
Fasting and PPBS and fasting and PP insulin levels 
Treatment
Find the underlying cause 
Reduce weight.  Glycolic acid cream at night 6-10% cream twice a week.
 Hydroquinone based creams twice a week
Creams such as demelan or biluma cream may help a little 
Home remedies:
 Uptan,
Potato juice.

Here are a few suggestions for common skin care concerns 

▪️Darkness around mouth 
Use agents which contain skin lightening agents like alpha arbutin, kojic acid and tranexemic acid . Use it twice a day 
Avoid toothpaste with menthol or pepermint. 
Recommendation: 
Suganda advanced pigmentation serum 

▪️Dark underarms 
Losing weight, avoiding tight clothing, friction and avoiding waxing helps in improving dark underarms. 
Use creams with lactic acid and urea twice a day to moisturise
Along  with a serum with glycolic acid for gentle exfoliation once or twice a week 
Recommendation: 
Dr. Sheth’s Gulab glycolic serum 
Suganda lactic acid body lotion 

▪️Uneven skin tone 
Usually tanning and dullness gives rise to skin tone looking uneven. Using antioxidant serums can help. Vitamin c is the most popular serum but if you cannot tolerate it , you can use something with resveratrol and ferulic acid .
Sunscreen is a must 
Recommendation: 
Raw beauty antioxidant serum 
Bioderma sunscreen 

▪️Dark neck 
Losing weight, avoiding friction and avoiding scrubbing can help in improving dark neck. 
Use creams with lactic acid to moisturise and gently exfoliate along with mild glycolic acid creams to remove dead skin layer. 
Recommendation: 
Sanfe spotlite cream 
The derma Co 4% urea moisturising cream

12 Things to remember about skin care in 2025. 

#2025 #skincare #dermatologist

Lakmé Sun expert event in Alibagh showcases all the new launches of sunscreen. 

@lakmeindia 

The theme was what’s your type to educate  about different sunscreens for different skin types; like cream based for dry skin and gel for oily skin. 

Sunscreens  help reduce dark spots, tanning , uneven skin tone and melasma. It also slows the process of ageing by reducing collagen breakdown and delaying formation of wrinkles.

Did you know that there can be a mismatch between the SPF written on the packaging and actual sunscreen . Yes that’s why it’s important to use products which under go proper testing. 

At the event , they demonstrated the efficacy of Lakmé sunscreens over other sunscreens which was quite interesting to see.

So, choose the right sunscreen for your skin type and use it regularly.
